title: Channel partner transformation in a post–COVID-19 world
itunes:title: Channel partner transformation in a post–COVID-19 world
description: The shift to XaaS is accelerating, and now, with COVID-19 continuing to shift business landscapes, how can technology channel partners around the world navigate this change and generate greater value for their enterprise customers?
